<p>Congrats on your move. I was just in Harvard Square a few days ago and enjoyed my short time walking around the area.</p>

<p>I will say, though, that while I was there, my ride on the T was delayed, some street musicians were playing loud Bob Dylan covers and, yes, I even witnessed some &#8220;homeless people begging.&#8221; I guess some things about city life are the same wherever you go.</p>

